OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FThe sister of a veteran who was killed
OL,8,Fon the RFA Sir Galahad has called on
OL,9,Fthe UK Government to release official
OL,10,Frecords which reveal how Argentinian
OL,11,Fbombers targeted the ship.
OL,13,FDocuments revealing the full facts
OL,14,Fabout the bombing are sealed until
OL,15,F2065 but families of those lost and
OL,16,Finjured want to understand why the
OL,17,Fattack, which killed 32 Welsh Guards,
OL,18,Fwas able to happen.
