OL,7,FThe ship and sister vessel Sir
OL,8,FTristram lost a total of 48 crew
OL,9,Fmembers, with many more injured.
OL,11,FAmong those who died was Peter
OL,12,FEdwards, aged 19, from Llandyrnog,
OL,13,Fnear Denbigh, who was described by his
OL,14,Fsisters Mandy Perkins and Barbara
OL,15,FRoyles as "full of life".
