OL,7,FIn April 1982, Argentine forces
OL,8,Finvaded the Falkland Islands, a
OL,9,FBritish overseas territory in the
OL,10,Fsouth-west Atlantic, and then Prime
OL,11,FMinister Margaret Thatcher sent a
OL,12,Ftaskforce to take them back.
OL,14,FWith the struggle to liberate the
OL,15,Fislands entering its closing stages in
OL,16,FJune, two RFAs - Sir Galahad and Sir
OL,17,FTristram - were sent to support the
OL,18,Ffinal assault.
