OL,7,FThey were due to deliver British
OL,8,Ftroops to Bluff Cove, but the ships
OL,9,Fdropped anchor five miles short of
OL,10,Ftheir destination at Fitzroy Sound.
OL,12,FArgentine forces subsequently bombed
OL,13,Fthe ships, and there was no greater
OL,14,FBritish loss of life throughout the
OL,15,FFalklands conflict than the attack.
OL,17,FBarbara Royles, one of Peter's
OL,18,Fsisters, told ITV Wales: "I've got
OL,19,Fpictures of Peter and he's always
OL,20,Flooking at me. He's always with us.
