OL,7,F"Nothing will be said or done to bring
OL,8,Fhim back but we just want closure on
OL,9,Fit because we won't be here to see it
OL,10,Fif they don't (release the documents).
OL,12,F"In 2065 we'll all be gone. We want
OL,13,Fjustice and closure."
OL,15,FUK Government defence minister Andrew
OL,16,FMurrison was asked about the
OL,17,Fpublication of all documents relating
OL,18,Fto the bombing of RFA Sir Galahad by
OL,19,FJessica Morden, Labour MP for Newport
OL,20,FEast in the House of Commons on 25
OL,21,FMarch.
