OL,7,FHe said: "I recognise the substantial
OL,8,Fpublic and parliamentary interest in
OL,9,Fthis matter. Consequently, I recently
OL,10,Fvisited the National Archives at Kew
OL,11,Fto view the RFA Sir Galahad files.
OL,13,F"As a result, we are looking to
OL,14,Frelease a further two files, subject
OL,15,Fto the legal advisers confirming that
OL,16,Findividuals' rights under the Data
OL,17,FProtection Act 2018 would not be
OL,18,Fcontravened.
