OL,7,F"In relation to the five files of
OL,8,Fwitness statements, I want maximum
OL,9,Ftransparency, subject to the Public
OL,10,FRecords Act 1958 and ensuring that
OL,11,Fpersonal data is protected. I shall
OL,12,Fprovide a further update shortly."
OL,14,FWhen pressed by Labour MP for Cardiff
OL,15,FSouth and Penarth, Stephen Doughty, on
OL,16,Fthe timeframe for this, the minister
OL,17,Fsaid: "I will not be drawn on precise
OL,18,Ftimes, but it will not be years."
